@startuml
title mulehang-agent 发送消息时序图

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam ParticipantPadding 20
skinparam BoxPadding 10
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

actor "用户" as user
participant "ChatScreen" as chatScreen
participant "ChatWindowState" as chatWindowState
participant "SendMessageUseCase" as sendMessageUseCase
participant "AgentGateway" as agentGateway
participant "KoogAgentGateway" as koogAgentGateway
participant "MulehangPromptExecutor" as promptExecutor
participant "AIAgent" as aiAgent

user -> chatScreen : 输入消息并点击 Send
chatScreen -> chatWindowState : send(message)

note right of chatWindowState
当前代码里 send(message) 仍是 TODO。
这里画的是设计上的目标主链路。
end note

chatWindowState -> sendMessageUseCase : invoke(prompt, activeProfile)
sendMessageUseCase -> sendMessageUseCase : 校验 prompt / profile
sendMessageUseCase -> agentGateway : run(prompt, profile)
agentGateway -> koogAgentGateway : 分派到具体实现

koogAgentGateway -> promptExecutor : buildPromptExecutor(config)
promptExecutor --> koogAgentGateway : MultiLLMPromptExecutor
koogAgentGateway -> aiAgent : 创建 AIAgent

koogAgentGateway --> sendMessageUseCase : Flow<Started>

group 后续目标
  koogAgentGateway -> aiAgent : 发送 prompt
  aiAgent --> koogAgentGateway : 增量/最终结果
  koogAgentGateway --> sendMessageUseCase : Flow<Delta>
  koogAgentGateway --> sendMessageUseCase : Flow<Completed>
end

alt 执行异常
  koogAgentGateway --> sendMessageUseCase : Flow<Failed>
end

sendMessageUseCase --> chatWindowState : 返回事件流
chatWindowState --> chatScreen : 更新消息列表与执行状态
chatScreen --> user : 渲染 Started / Delta / Completed / Failed

legend right
当前已实现：
1. SendMessageUseCase 参数校验
2. AgentGateway 抽象边界
3. KoogAgentGateway 内部创建 AIAgent / PromptExecutor

尚未完成：
1. ChatWindowState 对事件流的消费
2. 实际 prompt 发送
3. Delta / Completed 的产出与回写
endlegend

@enduml
